    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its life. The exterior is very clean, showing only light signs of road use such as minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact and free of major stains or tears, though there is some expected wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it is sound with a complete service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and all electronics functioning as intended. It is a reliable and presentable car that is ready for its next owner.",
