    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still has plenty of life left for all your weekend adventures. Everything runs smoothly, and the interior is looking really sharp! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
